  ('dietitian-moex-00176', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於醣類及其相關衍生物的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["菊糖（inulin）是一種果糖聚醣，溶於水，但無法被腸道酵素水解", "葡胺聚醣（glycosaminoglycans）是一種含有胺基糖及糖醛酸的多醣體", "玻尿酸（hyaluronic acid）是一種蛋白多醣（proteoglycans），具有緩衝或潤滑其他結構之作用", "醣蛋白（glycoprotein）及醣脂質（glycolipids）為細胞膜上重要的成分，其主要組成為葡萄糖"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c8c7112f23f9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "925f56d717e3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "102", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 29, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00177', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者為長期缺乏醣類可能引起的代謝作用異常？', '["促進酮酸生成", "促進肝醣合成", "抑制尿酸生成", "抑制葡萄糖合成"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c8c7112f23f9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "925f56d717e3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "102", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00178', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於肝醣磷酸化酶（glycogen phosphorylase）的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["升糖素（glucagon）可經由cyclic AMP之作用而刺激此酵素活性", "催化由肝醣非還原端釋出glucose-1-phosphate", "催化由肝醣α(1→6)鍵結進行磷酸裂解（phosphorolysis）", "此酵素之絲胺酸殘基（serine residue）磷酸化後才具活性"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c8c7112f23f9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "925f56d717e3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "102", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
