  ('dietitian-moex-00180', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於短鏈脂肪酸（short-chain fatty acids, SCFA）代謝的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["大腸中水溶性纖維經細菌發酵後可產生SCFA", "SCFA不須透過和膽鹽形成micelle而可在腸道被吸收", "SCFA被大腸吸收後可提供腸道細胞能量", "當SCFA進入粒線體進行氧化需要carnitine協助"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c8c7112f23f9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "925f56d717e3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "102", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00181', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於運動時能量代謝的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["低強度長時間的運動主要是進行glycolysis", "骨骼肌內會進行glycogenesis", "腎上腺素（epinephrine）促進脂肪組織的lipogenesis", "長時間的運動會進行脂肪酸β-oxidation"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c8c7112f23f9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "925f56d717e3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "102", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
